(12140, 1, '2018-02-12 16:11:13', '2018-02-12 15:11:13', 'For hhpberlin, Microsoft Dynamics 365 represents the technological foundation of its flexible organizational structure. Microsoft partner proMX assisted the company in the implementation. Dynamics 365 is not merely a customer management tool for hhpberlin. It’s also a place to collect all data and information that plays a role in its fire safety work and training sessions. This has resulted in an enormous reservoir of knowledge to which each employee now has access at any time from any location and device. In a few seconds, customer requests can be replied to and decisions made. For resource planning, too, hhpberlin uses Dynamics. Each employee has different talents, job experience and specific knowledge. To find the perfect person for a project, availability and skills of each resource are digitally checked, and results are yielded quickly. “This is one of the key features of Dynamics 365. It helps you to find and schedule the right resource,” says CEO Stefan Truthän. To manage projects, the fire protection experts have long used proRM Fast Start, the Dynamics compatible project management solution by proMX.', 'B2Run Nuremberg EN', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12118-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 16:11:13', '2018-02-12 15:11:13', '', 12118, 'http://promx.loc/2018/02/12118-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
