(10493, 1, '2017-03-27 13:45:43', '2017-03-27 13:45:43', '<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-10491\" src=\"http://promx.loc/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/proMX_at_CeBIT-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"proMX_at_CeBIT\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" />\r\n\r\nEvery year, IT experts from all over the world travel to CeBIT in Hannover, Germany. This year around 400,000 came to see what several thousand exhibitors, among them proMX, had in store.\r\n\r\nThis year, we were part of Microsoft’s Dynamics partner booth located in Hall 5. Microsoft had decided to present its solutions at several thematic partner booths as opposed to one big booth as in previous years. This meant that partners with their respective vertical focus and compatible solutions were at center stage.\r\n\r\n<strong>Managing customer relationships with Dynamics 365</strong>\r\n\r\nWe demonstrated the entire customer engagement functionality of Dynamics 365 – from sales and marketing to project management and customer service - to the numerous interested visitors to our booth.\r\n\r\nWe were happy to host hhpberlin as our reference customer at the fair. The engineering bureau for fire safety has long been affiliated with our company and is focused on continuous technological innovation. Not merely for the sake it but because the best IT equipment enables employees to perform at their best, emphasizes CEO Stefan Truthän.\r\n\r\nEspecially in the field of fire safety, digitalization harbors enormous potential. Hence, hhpberlin already uses IoT devices such as Microsoft HoloLens and Surface Hub for which it has developed its own apps. We brought both tools to Hannover in order to demonstrate their functionality and use with Dynamics 365.\r\n\r\n<strong>proMX looks forward to bringing this team and Dynamics 365 to Hannover Messe. We would be pleased to meet you there. </strong><a href=\"http://promx.loc/en/actions/live-experience/\"><strong>Register for a meeting today!</strong></a>', 'At CeBIT 2017 with Microsoft and hhpberlin', 'proMX was one of the Microsoft partners representing Dynamics 365 at CeBIT. We were joined at our booth by our customer hhpberlin.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'at-cebit-2017-with-microsoft-and-hhpberlin', '', '', '2017-03-29 08:21:44', '2017-03-29 08:21:44', '', 0, 'http://promx.loc/?p=10493', 0, 'post', '', 0),
