(10543, 1, '2017-04-18 14:05:21', '2017-04-18 14:05:21', '<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-10562\" src=\"http://promx.loc/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/en-1024x538.jpg\" alt=\"Hannover Messe\" width=\"1024\" height=\"538\" />\r\nproMX is among the 16 Microsoft partners that have been selected by the company to present its solutions at the world’s largest industrial fair. At our booth in Hall 7, we will introduce visitors to the intelligent business software Dynamics 365 and demonstrate how it can lead to more efficiency in sales, project management, customer and field service.\r\n\r\nDynamics 365 is especially beneficial to manufacturing companies. To stay competitive, it is paramount to produce economically and to remain flexible and agile. This is only possible if a company has transformed itself into a digital business. Then it can provide better service to its customers, optimize its processes and further develop its products.\r\n\r\nOur team will explain the different Dynamics 365 apps to you and how you can connect the solution to the Industrial Internet of Things. To demonstrate the latter, we will be hosting our customer hhpberlin at our booth. The fire safety engineers have, for example, developed an app for HoloLens, Microsoft’s mixed reality smartglasses.\r\n\r\n<strong>Visit us at Hannover Messe! Make your appointment <a href=\"http://promx.loc/en/interflex_and_hhpberlin/\">here</a>.</strong>', 'proMX as Microsoft Gold partner at Hannover Messe', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'promx-as-microsoft-gold-partner-at-hannover-messe', '', '', '2017-04-19 12:33:19', '2017-04-19 12:33:19', '', 0, 'http://promx.loc/?p=10543', 0, 'post', '', 0),
